&lt;p&gt;It is this expression causing the problem, right :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;     if ( ( getTarget() == null &amp;amp;&amp;amp; targetFilter == null ) || getTarget().equals( targetFilter ) )&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12773980" author="fmeschbe" created="Thu, 5 Nov 2009 17:14:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Implemented a guard against the NPE in Rev. 833085&lt;/p&gt;

